com.steelypip.powerups.hydranode

Class FlexiHydraNode<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,AttrValue,Field extends java.lang.Comparable<Field>,ChildValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.steelypip.powerups.hydranode.FlexiHydraNode<Key,AttrValue,Field,ChildValue>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HydraNode<Key,AttrValue,Field,ChildValue>, MultiAttributes<Key,AttrValue>, MultiLinks<Field,ChildValue>, Named, java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<Field,ChildValue>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlexiFusion, FlexiHydraXML

    public abstract class FlexiHydraNode<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,AttrValue,Field extends java.lang.Comparable<Field>,ChildValue>
extends java.lang.Object
implements HydraNode<Key,AttrValue,Field,ChildValue>
    This implementation provides a full implementation of all the mandatory and optional methods of the Hydra interface. It aims to strike a balance between fast access, update and reasonable compactness in the most important cases. The in-place mutating multi-maps are used to provide implementations that constantly adjust themselves to provide a good balance of speed and compactness.
